  "examinerNotes": "Moderate-severe DKA. Fixed rate insulin infusion (FRIII), IV 0.9% NaCl with careful K+ replacement, monitoring, DO NOT stop long-acting insulin, DO NOT use bicarbonate unless pH <6.9. Key error: stopping long-acting insulin, giving glucose before glucose <14mmol/L.",
